Package: whed
Title: Global Dataset on Higher Education Institutions
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Pablo", "Garcia-Guzman", email = "garciagp@ebrd.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides access to a comprehensive institution-level dataset on higher education institutions
    around the world, including various details such as institution names, 
    URLs, location, funding type, languages used, accrediting agencies, year founded, degrees offered, and more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
